of holiday gift books and discover all over again how wonderful so
many are. This year our enthusiastic volunteers share their
favorites among the photo books, anthologies and reference books.
Books _ carefully chosen _ seldom disappoint. An added pleasure is
that you, the giver, can read before you wrap. Here are some
recommended by various members of the Cox Newspaper family.
(Morris, Cox News Service) MOVED.
