   DOMESTIC-ABUSE _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ Sometimes, in the
shorthand people use when they have talked about something too many
times, Sandy will say, ``My husband kidnapped me and stabbed me and
tortured me and I almost died and God knows why I didn't.'' And
unless you already know the story, you think surely she must be
exaggerating. Because who on Earth could survive all that? This is
an incredibly emotional journey through one woman's life,
near-death and rebirth. (Evans, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
