Democrats relive their glory days of bringing down Nixon. By
Francis X. Clines.
</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH-LEGAL (Washington) _ An analysis of the defense
presented. By Jill Abramson.
</P>
<P>
   SCOTUS-SEARCH (Washington) _ A unanimous Supreme Court overturns
an Iowa law that permitted broad searches of vehicles after stops
for routine traffic violations. By Linda Greenhouse.
</P>
<P>
   SINATRA-FBI (Washington) _ The FBI releases 1,275 pages of files
it kept on Frank Sinatra, and the contents may settle once and for
all persistent questions about his rumored ties to the Mafia. By
Irvin Molotsky.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL-GENERAL &LR;  (Will move in ``a'' news file.)
