</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Unlike clothing, where everything old is new again,
verbal expressions, particularly slang, usually become extinct long
before the generation that coined them. For example, I never hear
anyone shouting ``Power to the people!'' or ``Way to go, Daddy-0!''
anymore. When was the last time you heard someone utter the words
