</P>
<P>
   Oh, by the way, it is almost Christmas time. Anyone for a touch
of forgiveness?
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (Amo Houghton is a Republican representative from New York and
the former chairman of Corning Inc.) &LR;
</P>
