keeping Gannon in the pocket.
</P>
<P>
   ``We are going to put a lot of emphasis on staying in the rush
lanes,'' Bates said. ``They have to be aware. But we don't want
them to be passive either. We want them to stay in the lanes with
aggressiveness.''
</P>
<P>
   And sack the quarterback.
</P>
</TEXT>
